  "comment_text": {
    "sn1.19:1.3": "At <a href='https://suttacentral.net/sn22.102/en/sujato#2.1'>SN 22.102:2.1</a> and <a href='https://suttacentral.net/an6.54/en/sujato#9.2'>AN 6.54:9.2</a>, <i lang='pi' translate='no'>santānakā</i> means “network of roots”, while at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/pli-tv-kd1/en/sujato#25.15.7'>Kd 1:25.15.7</a> it means “cobwebs”. "
